        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Fairness in Nursing Home Arbitration Act of 2012&nbsp;- Provides that a pre-dispute arbitration agreement between a long-term care facility and a resident (or anyone acting on the resident's behalf) shall not be valid or specifically enforceable.</p>]]></text>
